videos.description: Steph Curry keeps the Warriors' hot start going as he hits 3-pointers on back-to-back possessions.
videos.headline: Curry drills back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: Damian Lillard sends a cross-court pass to Carmelo Anthony, who knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner.
videos.headline: Lillard feeds Melo for 3-pointer

videos.description: Steph Curry finds a lane to the bucket and floats in a bucket while drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Curry floats in and-1

videos.description: Gary Trent Jr. makes his way past Kevon Looney for a layup and the foul.

videos.description: Steph Curry breezes to the rim and flips in an off-balanced layup while drawing contact.

videos.description: Damian Lillard drills a clutch, go-ahead 3-pointer late in the fourth quarter and then draws a charge on Draymond Green to help seal Portland's win.
